name: Distinct
description: Suppress duplicate items emitted by an Observable

name: Filter
description: Emit only those items from an Observable that pass a predicate test

name: IgnoreElements
description: Do not emit any items from an Observable but mirror its termination notification

name: SkipLast
description: Suppress the last n items emitted by an Observable

name: Skip
description: Suppress the first n items emitted by an Observable

name: TakeLast
description: Emit only the last n items emitted by an Observable

name: Take
description: Emit only the first n items emitted by an Observable
